---
title: GlowFrame — Key User Interaction Sequences
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    actor User
    participant LP as LightPage
    participant SM as SettingsModal
    participant Store as useAppStore
    participant LS as LightSurface
    participant FS as Fullscreen API
    participant WL as Wake Lock API

    Note over User,WL: App Startup

    LP->>WL: useWakeLock() — request('screen')
    WL-->>LP: lock acquired (screen stays on)
    Store->>Store: rehydrate from localStorage
    Store-->>LS: selectActiveProfile → render initial light

    Note over User,WL: Open Settings & Switch Mode

    User->>LP: click GearButton
    LP->>SM: open SettingsModal (isSettingsOpen = true)
    SM->>Store: read profiles[], activeProfileId
    Store-->>SM: profile list + active profile
    User->>SM: select new mode from dropdown
    SM->>Store: switchMode(id, "ring")
    Store->>Store: replace mode fields with MODE_DEFAULTS["ring"]
    Store-->>LS: selectActiveProfile → re-render as RingModeSurface
    LS-->>User: live light output updates instantly

    Note over User,WL: Adjust Settings (Live Preview)

    User->>SM: drag temperature/brightness slider
    SM->>Store: updateProfile(id, { lightTemperature: 4000 })
    Store-->>LS: selectActiveProfile → updated render
    LS-->>User: light colour/intensity updates in real time
    Store->>Store: persist to localStorage (debounced middleware)

    Note over User,WL: Manage Profiles

    User->>SM: click "New Profile"
    SM->>Store: createProfile("New Profile")
    Store->>Store: clone active profile → assign new UUID
    Store->>Store: set activeProfileId = new UUID
    Store-->>SM: updated profile list (new profile highlighted)
    User->>SM: type new name in name input, blur
    SM->>Store: renameProfile(id, "Studio Warm")
    User->>SM: click a different profile in list
    SM->>Store: setActiveProfile(otherId)
    Store-->>LS: different profile rendered immediately
    User->>SM: click delete on a profile
    SM->>Store: deleteProfile(id)
    Store->>Store: fallback to previous/adjacent profile

    Note over User,WL: Fullscreen Toggle

    User->>LP: press "f" key (not in text input)
    LP->>FS: useFullscreen().toggle()
    FS-->>LP: fullscreenchange event fires
    LP->>LP: isFullscreen state synced
    LP-->>User: FullscreenButton icon updates (Maximize2 ↔ Minimize2)

    Note over User,WL: Tab Hidden → Tab Visible (Wake Lock)

    User->>LP: switch browser tab (page hidden)
    LP->>WL: release wake lock (visibilitychange → hidden)
    User->>LP: return to tab (page visible)
    LP->>WL: re-acquire wake lock (visibilitychange → visible)
